## 💡 Key Concepts
- `trigger:` defines when pipeline runs automatically
- `pool: vmImage` selects a Microsoft-hosted agent
- `PublishTestResults@2` shows results in the Azure DevOps UI
- `condition: always()` publishes results even on failure
